    <item>
      <title>Coatue 的 Laffont 表示他对人工智能的潜力感到兴奋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/coatue-s-laffont-says-he-s-excited-about-potential-for-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁、Coatue Management 创始人 Philippe Laffont 表示，他看好人工智能，因为每个人都在谈论人工智能，这可能是一个好兆头。他在纽约彭博投资峰会上接受 David Rubenstein 采访时发表了上述言论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/coatue-s-laffont-says-he-s-excited-about-potential-for-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:28:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼集团将斥资 156 亿美元推进绿色基础设施建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/adani-group-to-spend-15-6-billion-in-green-infrastructure-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿达尼集团今年将把资本支出增加一倍，加快对港口、机场和道路等绿色能源和基础设施项目的投资，这再次表明该企业集团已经摆脱了负面卖空报告的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/adani-group-to-spend-15-6-billion-in-green-infrastructure-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:27:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果罢工持续，埃克森美孚可能不得不停止法国炼油厂的生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/exxon-may-have-to-halt-french-oil-refinery-if-strike-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司表示，如果罢工持续下去，该公司可能不得不关闭位于法国北部的格拉旺雄炼油厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/exxon-may-have-to-halt-french-oil-refinery-if-strike-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:24:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃克森美孚签署协议，向韩国电池巨头供应锂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/exxon-signs-deal-to-supply-lithium-to-south-korean-battery-giant-sk-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司签署了一项初步协议，向韩国电池制造商 SK On Co. 供应其在阿肯色州开发的锂矿，此举加深了这家石油巨头与快速发展的电动汽车行业的联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/exxon-signs-deal-to-supply-lithium-to-south-korean-battery-giant-sk-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:20:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁 Wiese 的 Brait 计划在三年内逐步缩减投资组合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/billionaire-wiese-s-brait-plans-to-wind-down-portfolio-within-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Brait SE 是一家由亿万富翁克里斯托·维塞 (Christo Wiese) 支持的南非投资控股公司，该公司预计将在未来 18 个月至三年内出售其现有投资组合并向投资者返还资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/billionaire-wiese-s-brait-plans-to-wind-down-portfolio-within-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>托兹称拜登胜选可能比特朗普更扰乱市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/biden-win-could-disrupt-markets-more-than-trump-tooze-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济历史学家亚当·图兹表示，即使乔·拜登赢得第二任期，美国严重的党派分歧也可能给市场带来不确定性。这是因为如果他再次击败唐纳德·特朗普，共和党人可能会更加猛烈地抨击他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/biden-win-could-disrupt-markets-more-than-trump-tooze-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 12:45:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行为其债券投资组合设定更严格的气候目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/ecb-says-it-s-gradually-cutting-co2-emissions-from-its-portfolio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行表示，作为其货币政策更加绿色的计划的一部分，它可能会重新平衡未实现气候目标的投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/ecb-says-it-s-gradually-cutting-co2-emissions-from-its-portfolio</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
